About the Course

Struggling with DSA? Join the 30 Days DSA Bootcamp, where we break down Data Structures and Algorithms into simple, beginner-friendly lessons. Each day, you'll learn a new concept, solve coding problems, and build a strong foundation for interviews and competitive programming.

What to Expect?

✅ Daily Learning Plan – Covering fundamental to advanced DSA topics.
✅ 15+ Theory & Coding Articles – In-depth content that breaks down complex concepts with examples and solutions.
✅ Hands-on Practice – Solve 100+ problems on Unstop.
✅ 5+ Role-Based Assessments – Tailored tests for different job roles to help you target your career goals.
✅ Optimized Approaches – Learn brute force & efficient solutions for every problem.
✅ Interview Readiness – Real-world coding scenarios and company-specific questions.
✅ Doubt Support – Get expert guidance to resolve queries.

🎓 Bonus Perks:

✅ Become DSA-ready in just 30 days and build a strong problem-solving mindset.
✅ Earn a certificate of completion to showcase your achievement.
✅ Boost your resume and make your profile stand out to recruiters.
✅ Enhance your LinkedIn profile with a recognized certification.
✅ Gain the confidence to tackle coding interviews and competitive programming challenges.

Because what’s better than mastering DSA? Mastering it with proof!
